trans-unit.source: List Cloud Services
trans-unit.target: List Cloud Services

trans-unit.source: The <languageKeyword>List Cloud Services</languageKeyword> operation lists the cloud services that are available under the specified subscription.
trans-unit.target: The <languageKeyword>List Cloud Services</languageKeyword> operation lists the cloud services that are available under the specified subscription.

trans-unit.source: DefaultWinRMCertificateThumbprint
trans-unit.target: DefaultWinRMCertificateThumbprint

trans-unit.source: Specifies the default certificate for a secure connection with WinRM.
trans-unit.target: Specifies the default certificate for a secure connection with WinRM.

trans-unit.source: If a certificate thumbprint is not specified for WinRM when a Virtual Machine is deployed in a cloud service, a certificate is automatically created and the thumbprint is listed as the value of this element.
trans-unit.target: If a certificate thumbprint is not specified for WinRM when a Virtual Machine is deployed in a cloud service, a certificate is automatically created and the thumbprint is listed as the value of this element.

trans-unit.source: For more information about defining WinRM, see <externalLink><linkText>Create Virtual Machine Deployment</linkText><linkUri>http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/jj157194.aspx</linkUri></externalLink> or <externalLink><linkText>Add Role</linkText><linkUri>http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/jj157186.aspx</linkUri></externalLink>.
trans-unit.target: For more information about defining WinRM, see <externalLink><linkText>Create Virtual Machine Deployment</linkText><linkUri>http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/jj157194.aspx</linkUri></externalLink> or <externalLink><linkText>Add Role</linkText><linkUri>http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/jj157186.aspx</linkUri></externalLink>.

trans-unit.source: Specifies the roles sizes that are available for deployments in the cloud service.
trans-unit.target: Specifies the roles sizes that are available for deployments in the cloud service.

trans-unit.source: The available role sizes are defined by the resources that are supported by the cloud service.
trans-unit.target: The available role sizes are defined by the resources that are supported by the cloud service.

trans-unit.source: For example, deployments of web roles and worker roles may have different sizes available than deployments of Virtual Machines.
trans-unit.target: For example, deployments of web roles and worker roles may have different sizes available than deployments of Virtual Machines.

trans-unit.source: Remarks
trans-unit.target: Remarks

trans-unit.source: If the <parameterReference>x-ms-version</parameterReference> is older than 2012-03-01, cloud services that contain virtual machine deployments will not be returned.
trans-unit.target: If the <parameterReference>x-ms-version</parameterReference> is older than 2012-03-01, cloud services that contain virtual machine deployments will not be returned.

trans-unit.source: You can see the cloud services that exist in your subscription by looking in the Cloud Services section of the Management Portal.

trans-unit.target: You can also get a list of cloud services by using the <externalLink><linkText>Get-AzureService</linkText><linkUri>http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/jj152880.aspx</linkUri></externalLink> cmdlet.
